CULTURAL ACKNOWLEDGMENT:

The names and concepts of the "Eight Extraordinary Skills" (Ba Qi Ji / Hachigiki)
used in this project are derived from the Chinese manga "The Outliers" (Yi Ren Zhi Xia /
Hitori no Shita) created by Mi Er. These cultural references are used for educational
and technical community purposes only. All rights to the original work belong to
Mi Er and the respective publishers.

This project does not claim any ownership of the original creative work and
acknowledges that the cultural elements are the intellectual property of their
creators. Commercial use of these specific cultural references may require
separate authorization from the rights holders.
